Hearthstone Battlegrounds. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored
by, or approved by Blizzard Entertainment, HearthSim, Hearthstone Deck
Tracker, Firestone, Zero to Heroes, Gamerhub, or HSReplay.

The root MIT LICENSE applies only to original Bob Coach code and original
